OL,3,C3,500 riders at Galloway forest park
OL,4,Cfor world-class cycling event
OL,6,FAround 3,500 cyclists will be in south
OL,7,Fwest Scotland this weekend, for one of
OL,8,Fthe top events of its kind in Europe.
OL,10,FThe Gralloch will be at Galloway
OL,11,Fforest park from Friday 15 May until
OL,12,FSunday 17 May.
OL,14,FElite cyclists will compete in the UCI
OL,15,Frace on Saturday, which is 323km in
OL,16,Fdistance. It's for a chance to qualify
OL,17,Ffor the UCI gravel world championships.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
