OL,3,C3,500 riders at Galloway forest park
OL,4,Cfor world-class cycling event
OL,6,FAmateur riders can also enjoy the
OL,7,Fweekend festival, cycling along gravel
OL,8,Fpaths around the forest and taking in
OL,9,Fthe views.
OL,11,FMore than 4,000 visitors are expected
OL,12,Fto attend The Gralloch.
OL,14,FOrganisers say it is yet another
OL,15,Fexample of the South of Scotland
OL,16,Fputting itself forward as a premier
OL,17,Fcycling destination.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
