OL,3,C3,500 riders at Galloway forest park
OL,4,Cfor world-class cycling event
OL,6,FEvent organiser Maximilian Wussler
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think we have the perfect mix
OL,8,Fhere because often you have a
OL,9,Fbeautiful place that doesn't have the
OL,10,Ftracks available or the access
OL,11,Favailable to do event like this, but
OL,12,Fhere we found the perfect mixture it's
OL,13,Fgot the tracks, its got the scenery.
OL,15,F"You know, just driving in here, it's
OL,16,Fthe first time you see the coast as
OL,17,Fwell. It is a beautiful part of the
OL,18,Fworld, and we are excited to showcase
OL,19,Fit to a global audience."
